essed be the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You who ride on white "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Hb obscure"},{"kind":"text","text":" donkeys,"},{"kind":"text","text":" who sit on saddle blankets,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and who travel on the road, give praise!"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Hb obscure"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Let them tell the righteous acts "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 12:7","book":"1Sa","chapter":12,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 103:6","book":"Psa","chapter":103,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 45:24","book":"Isa","chapter":45,"verse":24,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mc 6:5","book":"Mic","chapter":6,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"text","text":" the righteous deeds of his villagers in Israel,"},{"kind":"text","text":" with the voices of the singers at the watering places. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Hb obscure"},{"kind":"text","text":" Then the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s people went down to the city gates."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Sm 12:7","book":"1Sa","chapter":12,"verse":7},{"label":"Ps 103:6","book":"Psa","chapter":103,"verse":6},{"label":"Is 45:24","book":"Isa","chapter":45,"verse":24},{"label":"Mc 6:5","book":"Mic","chapter":6,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Hb obscure"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Awake! Awake, Deborah!"},{"kind":"text","text":" Awake! Awake, sing a song!"},{"kind":"text","text":" Arise, Barak,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and take your prisoners,"},{"kind":"text","text":" son of Abinoam!”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then the survivors "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 21:35","book":"Num","chapter":21,"verse":35,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 2:34","book":"Deu","chapter":2,"verse":34,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 1:9","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" came down to the nobles; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 5:25","book":"Jdg","chapter":5,"verse":25,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 23:20","book":"2Ch","chapter":23,"verse":20,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 3:5","book":"Neh","chapter":3,"verse":5,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 10:29","book":"Neh","chapter":10,"verse":29,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 16:3","book":"Psa","chapter":16,"verse":3,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 14:3","book":"Jer","chapter":14,"verse":3,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nah 2:5","book":"Nam","chapter":2,"verse":5,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Na 3:18","book":"Nam","chapter":3,"verse":18,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"text","text":" the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"’s people came down to me "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"LXX reads down for him"},{"kind":"text","text":" against the warriors."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Nm 21:35","book":"Num","chapter":21,"verse":35},{"label":"Dt 2:34","book":"Deu","chapter":2,"verse":34},{"label":"Is 1:9","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":9},{"label":"Jdg 5:25","book":"Jdg","chapter":5,"verse":25},{"label":"2Ch 23:20","book":"2Ch","chapter":23,"verse":20},{"label":"Neh 3:5","book":"Neh","chapter":3,"verse":5},{"label":"Neh 10:29","book":"Neh","chapter":10,"verse":29},{"label":"Ps 16:3","book":"Psa","chapter":16,"verse":3},{"label":"Jr 14:3","book":"Jer","chapter":14,"verse":3},{"label":"Nah 2:5","book":"Nam","chapter":2,"verse":5},{"label":"Na 3:18","book":"Nam","chapter":3,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"LXX reads down for him"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Those with their roots in Amalek "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"LXX reads in the valley"},{"kind":"text","text":" came from Ephraim;"},{"kind":"text","text":" Benjamin came with your people after you."},{"kind":"text","text":" The leaders came down from Machir, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 50:23","book":"Gen","chapter":50,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 26:29","book":"Num","chapter":26,"verse":29,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 32:39–40","book":"Num","chapter":32,"verse":39,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jos 17:1","book":"Jos","chapter":17,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 9:4","book":"2Sa","chapter":9,"verse":4,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" and those who carry a marshal’s staff came from Zebulun."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 50:23","book":"Gen","chapter":50,"verse":23},{"label":"Nm 26:29","book":"Num","chapter":26,"verse":29},{"label":"Nm 32:39–40","book":"Num","chapter":32,"verse":39},{"label":"Jos 17:1","book":"Jos","chapter":17,"verse":1},{"label":"2Sm 9:4","book":"2Sa","chapter":9,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"LXX reads in the valley"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The princes of Issachar were with Deborah;"},{"kind":"text","text":" Issachar was with Barak;"},{"kind":"text","text":" they were under his leadership "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit they set out as his feet"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 4:10","book":"Jdg","chapter":4,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the valley."},{"kind":"text","text":" There was great searching "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss, Syr read There were great resolves"},{"kind":"text","text":" of heart"},{"kind":"text","text":" among the clans of Reuben."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jdg 4:10","book":"Jdg","chapter":4,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit they set out as his feet"},{"marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss, Syr read There were great resolves"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Why did you sit among the sheep pens "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or the campfires"},{"kind":"text","text":" listening to the playing of pipes for the flocks?"},{"kind":"text","text":" There was great searching of heart"},{"kind":"text","text":" among the clans of Reuben."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or the campfires"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Gilead "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 31:25","book":"Gen","chapter":31,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 32:40","book":"Num","chapter":32,"verse":40,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 10:17","book":"Jdg","chapter":10,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" remained beyond the Jordan."},{"kind":"text","text":" Dan, why did you linger at the ships?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Asher remained at the seashore"},{"kind":"text","text":" and stayed in his harbors."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 31:25","book":"Gen","chapter":31,"verse":25},{"label":"Nm 32:40","book":"Num","chapter":32,"verse":40},{"label":"Jdg 10:17","book":"Jdg","chapter":10,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The people of Zebulun defied death,"},{"kind":"text","text":" Naphtali also, on the heights of the battlefield."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Kings came and fought."},{"kind":"text","text":" Then the kings of Canaan fought"},{"kind":"text","text":" at Taanach by the Waters of Megiddo,"},{"kind":"text","text":" but they did not plunder the silver."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The stars fought from the heavens;"},{"kind":"text","text":" the stars fought with Sisera from their paths."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The river Kishon swept them away, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 4:15","book":"Jdg","chapter":4,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" the ancient river, the river Kishon."},{"kind":"text","text":" March on, my soul, in strength!"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jdg 4:15","book":"Jdg","chapter":4,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The horses’ hooves then hammered —"},{"kind":"text","text":" the galloping, galloping of his "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"= Sisera’s"},{"kind":"text","text":" stallions."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"= Sisera’s"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Curse Meroz,” says the angel of the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"text","text":" “Bitterly curse her inhabitants,"},{"kind":"text","text":" for they did not come to help the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"text","text":" to help the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" with the warriors.”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Most blessed of women is Jael,"},{"kind":"text","text":" the wife of Heber the Kenite;"},{"kind":"text","text":" she is most blessed among tent-dwelling women."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He asked for water; she gave him milk."},{"kind":"text","text":" She brought him cream "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 18:8","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:14","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 17:29","book":"2Sa","chapter":17,"verse":29,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 20:17","book":"Job","chapter":20,"verse":17,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 29:6","book":"Job","chapter":29,"verse":6,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 30:3","book":"Pro","chapter":30,"verse":3,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 7:15","book":"Isa","chapter":7,"verse":15,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 7:22","book":"Isa","chapter":7,"verse":22,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" in a majestic bowl."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 18:8","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":8},{"label":"Dt 32:14","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":14},{"label":"2Sm 17:29","book":"2Sa","chapter":17,"verse":29},{"label":"Jb 20:17","book":"Job","chapter":20,"verse":17},{"label":"Jb 29:6","book":"Job","chapter":29,"verse":6},{"label":"Pr 30:3","book":"Pro","chapter":30,"verse":3},{"label":"Is 7:15","book":"Isa","chapter":7,"verse":15},{"label":"Is 7:22","book":"Isa","chapter":7,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"She reached for a tent peg,"},{"kind":"text","text":" her right hand, for a workman’s hammer."},{"kind":"text","text":" Then she hammered Sisera —"},{"kind":"text","text":" she crushed his head;"},{"kind":"text","text":" she shattered and pierced his temple."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He collapsed, he fell, he lay down between her feet;"},{"kind":"text","text":" he collapsed, he fell between her feet;"},{"kind":"text","text":" where he collapsed, there he fell —dead."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Sisera’s mother looked through the window;"},{"kind":"text","text":" she peered through the lattice, crying out:"},{"kind":"text","text":" “Why is his chariot so long in coming?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Why don’t I hear the hoofbeats of his horses?” "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit Why have the hoofbeats of his chariots delayed"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit Why have the hoofbeats of his chariots delayed"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Her wisest princesses answer her;"},{"kind":"text","text":" she even answers herself:"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Are they not finding and dividing the spoil —"},{"kind":"text","text":" a girl or two "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit a womb or two wombs"},{"kind":"text","text":" for each warrior,"},{"kind":"text","text":" the spoil of colored garments for Sisera,"},{"kind":"text","text":" the spoil of an embroidered garment or two for my neck?” "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Hb obscure"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit a womb or two wombs"},{"marker":1,"text":"Hb obscure"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jdg:5:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", may all your enemies perish as Sisera did. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit perish in this way"},{"kind":"text","text":" But may those who love him"},{"kind":"text","text":" be like the rising of the sun in its strength."},{"kind":"text","text":" And the land had peace for forty years."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit perish in this way"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783279378019}